Automated Arch Linux installation
=================================

Boot Arch ISO and follow:
1. Boot
2. wifi-menu
3. curl -L https://github.com/jimenezrick/arch-install/archive/master.tar.gz | tar xfz -
4. arch-install-master/run.sh


Manual steps post-installation
------------------------------
1. Restore /etc and /home with extra/ scripts.
2. Restore /usr/local, install:
   - dwm
   - dmenu
   - dwmstatus
3. Install AUR packages using cower.
